Package: modelpod
Type: Package
Title: Point of departure estimation with natural splines
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Simple point of departure estimation. Fits a 3 d.f. natural spline lm(y ~ splines::ns(x, df = 3))
    and uses user defined response value plus the upper 95% confidence limit of the regression fit
    to estimate the point of departure. A '../results' folder is returned containing
    a pdf with the fitted curves and a tab delimited text file with the estimates.
    
License: What license is it under?
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    splines (>= 3.5.1)
